As the error said, you should add import to essentials. The import should be what you added with `com.earth2me.essentials`, but it also should be the repository where the dependency is.

For this, you add this into your `build.gradle` file:
```
repositories {
    maven {
        url &quot;https://repo.essentialsx.net/releases/&quot;
        name &quot;Essentials releases&quot;
    }
}
```

If you want snapshot (which is not your case here), you should add this:
```
repositories {
    maven {
        url &quot;https://repo.essentialsx.net/snapshots/&quot;
        name &quot;Essentials releases&quot;
    }
}
```
[Documentation](https://essentialsx.net/wiki/Common-Issues.html)

